high_descs: Turn right, move to the stove.
Pick up the potato in the trash can sitting left of the stove.
Turn around, bring the potato to the microwave in the right corner.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Bring the heated potato back to the trash can behind you to the left.
Put the heated potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right and around the island to the left to the gray trash can on the floor at the end of the counter.
Take out the potato in the trash can.
Turn left and go around the island to the microwave on the other side of the kitchen.
After heating potato, remove it from the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the gray trash can on the floor.
Place the potato in the trash can.
anns.task_desc: Throw out a heated potato in the trash can.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the trash can by the window
Pick up the potato from the trash can
Turn left and go around the island counter to the microwave
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it off. Take the potato out of the microwave
Turn around and walk around the island counter to the trash can
Put the potato in the trash can
anns.task_desc: Put a heated potato in the trash
